com.uce.userlab.haptics.motion.event
Class PlayerEventSupport

java.lang.Object
  com.uce.userlab.haptics.motion.event.PlayerEventSupport

public class PlayerEventSupport
extends java.lang.Object

This supports the Player implementations with manageing PlayerListeners and event calls to those PlayerListeners. It provides methods for firing all events for a standard PlayerListener to detect and number of variables that can be povided with the event fire.
